{
  "stem": "18654.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 329.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't remember the arrival of the boat, but I remember arriving in London because of the big red buses, which we'd, of course, never seen before.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were all taken to a hall where we awaited to be picked up by the various people that had agreed to take us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We weren't allowed-- we were allowed to take what a child could carry, which was very little-- one suitcase and one little case.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That a child couldn't carry much more than that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that is what I carried.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I really-- my biggest memory were leibchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you know what ein leibchen is?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a liberty bodice, which was the most strange garment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And garments that were all-in-one, that you had great difficulty unbuttoning when necessary, [LAUGHS] because it buttoned up across the back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you had quite a problem with this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember I had a rain cape, which nobody-- no children in England had, and it used to embarrass me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a cape with a hood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the usual absolute necessities were in that case.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Only the necessities, because that's all you could carry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I have a list of this, which perhaps will be shown on camera, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were several things that were confiscated from that list.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was just some few little bits of pathetic jewelry were taken away from us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Apart from that, that's all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I suppose I had my doll.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm sure I must have had a doll, because I loved my toys.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I can't remember any more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you know this has gone completely from my memory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All I can remember is them taking me and being at the station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't-- I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
